<div id="Idea_3915"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3915-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3915">Stop trying to pass excessive agendas such as health care and cap and trade during economic hardships&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
